Class CatSnapshot

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.martynatyran.domain.cat.dto.CatSnapshot

  • public class CatSnapshot
extends java.lang.Object
    A class that is a Data Transfer Object for Cat Entity. Provides all only getters of Cat Entity values so that the entity could not be modified.
